{
  "texts": [
    "We also use Pingdingshan Tian'an Coal Industry Co., Ltd.-the first Chinese coal enterprise to issue green bonds-to verify our findings.",
    "The company received extensive positive reports from Henan Province and the media.",
    "foot_5 As a result, research Hypothesis 3 is supported.",
    "We confirmed the positive relationship between green bond issuance and ER using the SDID approach and a host of robustness checks in the above empirical analysis.",
    "Furthermore, this study investigates whether green bonds have heterogeneous impacts on ER in different enterprises and industries and the economic impact on enterprise value."
  ]
}